{"tid":1319014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最新】兩危殆傷者轉為情況嚴重及穩定","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:30:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"96f94ab79d3d0d028bd65407f4581b26845828b1","tid":1319014,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂風波未平息，昨日(14日)沙田區反修例結束後再爆發激烈警民衝突，多人受傷。醫管局表示，有28名男女被送院，<span style=\"color: red;\">而截至今早11時半，尚有7名男傷者需要留醫，而早前2名危殆傷者情況已轉為嚴重及穩定。</span><br />\n<br />\n目前7名留院的傷者中，仍然有2人情況嚴重，5人情況穩定，分別在沙田威爾斯親王醫院及大埔那打素醫院留醫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5Qg8vT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5Qg8vT.jpg&h=378ae316&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ec7628bf00bb2a307dd300e0ffd46628a3fb7cf","tid":1319014,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"港共期待緊死第一個警察或者示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1318968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1318968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"56b21d23de7c8830d004faf0c6a0cf425a68b9ec","tid":1319014,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee3c6b7a24561e573fa8e0ac180a7cce4f810a9","tid":1319014,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9089cdfe4df484ceb08b11dcc47fabebf22d10","tid":1319014,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ecb1d0116892671ebcf1d19b3369603b23b224","tid":1319014,"uid":93908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"義士無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/